get.summary: Search for sales statistics in a given geographic level.
get.description:
- Standard Auction Clearance Rate formula is: `AuctionNumberSold / (AuctionNumberAuctioned + AuctionNumberWithdrawn)`
- The Rate is considered Not Statistic Reliable if: `AuctionNumberAuctioned + AuctionNumberWithdrawn < 10`
- APM Standard Gross Rental Yield formula is: `(MedianRentListingPrice* 52) / MedianSoldPrice`
- The Yield is considered Not Available if: `MedianRentListingPrice is null or MedianSoldPrice is null`

parameters.name: state
parameters.description: The Australian state abbreviation

parameters.name: suburb
parameters.description: Suburb name to retrieve data for

parameters.name: periodSize
parameters.description: Unit of the measurement period to use

parameters.name: startingPeriodRelativeToCurrent
parameters.description: When to start stats from. 1 = current period, 2 = previous period, etc.

parameters.name: totalPeriods
parameters.description: Number of total periods to show statistics for. i.e. 4 Quarters would be 1 full year

supplementary.description:
Rural attributes

*Improvements* (optional)

Available `types` (fixed list, optional):
* Machinery Shed
* Shearing Shed
* Workshop
* Shearers Quarters
* Silos
* Other Housing
* Managers Accommodation

*Fencing* (optional)

`description` (string, optional): free text fencing description, maximum 250 characters.

*Yards* (optional)

Available `types` (fixed list, optional):
* Sheep
* Cattle

*Homestead* (optional)

`description` (string, optional): description of the homestead and construction, maximum 250 characters.

`metadata` (optional)
* `area` (decimal, optional): homestead area in square metres.

Available `types` (fixed list, optional):
* Office
* Ensuite
* Tennis Court
* Mains Gas
* Floorboards
* Internal Laundry

*Water* (optional)

`description` (string, optional): water comments, maximum 250 characters.

Available `types` (fixed list, optional):
* Tank
* Well
* Reticulated
* Bores
* Springs
* Creeks
* Dams
* River

*Crops* (optional)

`description` (string, optional): description of the crops, maximum 250 characters.

`metadata` (optional)
* `croppedAnnually` (decimal, optional): average annual area cropped in hectares.
* `fallowAnnually` (decimal, optional): average annual fallow area in hectares.
* `pastures` (string, optional): description of pastures available, maximum 250 characters.

*Livestock* (optional)

`description` (string, optional): additional comments, maximum 250 characters.

`metadata` (optional)
* `capacity` (decimal, optional): property carrying capacity in DSE (unit of carry capacity).

Available `types` (fixed list, optional):
* Sheep
* Pigs
* Cattle
* Poultry
* Horses
* Exotic
* Goats
* Stud

*Inclusions* (optional)

`description` (string, optional): description of plant and machinery included in sale, maximum 250 characters.

`metadata` (optional)
* `livestock` (string, optional): description of livestock included in sale, maximum 250 characters.
* `crop` (string, optional): description of crops included in sale, maximum 250 characters.

*Irrigation* (optional)

`description` (string, optional): irrigation comments, maximum 250 characters

`metadata` (optional)
* `rainfall` (decimal, optional): annual rainfall in millimetres.

Listings.v2.Objective.description: The advertisement's objective  * `Sale` - Residential Advertisement for Sale * `Rent` - Residential Advertisement for Rent

Listings.v2.Status.description: The lifecycle status of a Listing  * `Unknown` - The listing has an unknown status, this can only be the case if data is somehow corrupted. * `Archived` - The listing has been archived and is inactive. * `UnderOffer` - An offer has been made for the listing. The listing is still active. * `Sold` - The listing has been sold.             The listing is inactive but may appear as sold listing on Domain * `Leased` - The listing has been leased. * `NewDevelopment` - The listing is a New Development Listing.             The listing is active. * `RecentlyUpdated` - The listing or project has been updated in past few days.             The listing is active. * `New` - The listing or project has been created in past few days.             The listing is active. * `Live` - The listing or project is currently live and has not been recently created or updated.             This listing is active. * `Pending` - This status is only used by projects.             It indicates that the project is pending to be activated (start date in the future).             This project is inactive. * `DepositTaken` - Deposit Taken. This listing is still active.

to.description: Highest price the property is expected to sell/rent for to set search price.

comparableProperty.description: Comparable properties that are of a similar standard or condition to the property for sale

declarationText.description: Text description if there are less than three comparable sales available

Listings.V2.ComparableData.description: Information regarding the past comparable property sales that influenced the setting of the estimation price

Listings.v2.MedianPriceType.description: Type of the median price type  * `House` - House * `ApartmentUnitFlat` - Apartment / unit / flat * `VacantLand` - Vacant Land

suburb.description: Name of the suburb median price is based on.

source.description: Where median price data comes from

sourceDateFrom.description: Start date of the median price source time period

sourceDateTo.description: End date of the median price source time period

sourceCollectionDate.description: The collection date of the median price source

Listings.V2.MedianPriceData.description: Information regarding median house/unit price   for the suburb

documentationUrl.description: Link to the statement of information documentation file

Listings.V2.StatementOfInformation.description: Statement of Information  Regarding sale listing

id.description: The identifier which uniquely identifies the listing.

bathrooms.description: Total number of bathrooms in the property

bedrooms.description: Total number of bedrooms in the property; Studio apartments have a value of \"0\"

buildingArea.description: The building area display value of the property e.g. 160 ha

buildingAreaSqm.description: The properties building area in square meters

carspaces.description: Total number of car spaces in the property.

dateAvailable.description: The date the property is available. DateTime is in AEST (Australian Eastern Standard Time) timezone.

dateCreated.description: The date/time the listing was created. DateTime is in AEST (Australian Eastern Standard Time) timezone.

dateUpdated.description: The date/time the listing had major update. DateTime is in AEST (Australian Eastern Standard Time) timezone.

dateMinorUpdated.description: When minor update applied to listing. DateTime is in AEST (Australian Eastern Standard Time) timezone.

datePurged.description: The date/time the listing was purged. It's only returned for archived listings. DateTime is in AEST (Australian Eastern Standard Time) timezone.

dateListed.description: The date/time last listed. DateTime is in AEST (Australian Eastern Standard Time) timezone.

description.description: The long description of the property provided by the advertiser

devProjectId.description: The ID of the development project - null if no associated project

energyEfficiencyRating.description: Energy Efficiency Rating value for ACT properties

features.description: The property features specified by the advertiser

headline.description: The short description of the property provided by the advertiser

isNewDevelopment.description: Indicates whether the property is a new development

landArea.description: The land area display string for the property e.g. 160 sqm

landAreaSqm.description: The properties land area in square meters

media.description: The media associated with the property provided by the advertiser

propertyId.description: The identifier which uniquely identifies the property being advertised.   This may be empty if the Address of property is poorly described

isWithdrawn.description: Indicates if the property has been withdrawn from the market  The value will be 'true' When a listing is taken off market without being sold or leased.

homepassEnabled.description: If Homepass is enabled for the listing (agency)

numberOfDwellings.description: Number of dwellings for current listing

providerSystem.description: Identify the source of the listing

streetNumber.description: Street (and possibly unit) number component of an address. E.g. 23, 1a, 11/1.

contactIds.description: Identifier of each contact the advertiser has associated with the listing

agentIds.description: Identifier of each agent the advertiser has associated with the listing

from.description: Lower end of the price range.

to.description: Upper end of the price range.

displayText.description: When provided this will be shown instead of the price range, e.g.: "Offers over $450K considered"

PreMarket.v1.GeoLocation.description: Encapsulates the details of a geo location.

documentationUrl.description:
Link to the statement of information documentation file.
Must be a PDF file.
File should be less than 10 MB in size
The Statement of Information must be updated if there is a change in the indicative selling price.

bedrooms.description: Total number of bedrooms in the property

bathrooms.description: Total number of bathrooms in the property

carspaces.description: Total number of car spaces in the property.

headline.description: The short description of the property provided by the advertiser

description.description: The long description of the property provided by the advertiser

authorityExecutedDate.description:
The date on which the authority contract was executed.
The date is compliant with the ISO 8601 and is in the UTC format, e.g. 2009-06-15T13:45:30.0000000Z.

propertyTypes.description: The property types (e.g. house, apartment/unit/flat, etc.).

exclusivePeriodDays.description: The time (in days) that the agent has exclusive authority to sell the property.

exclusiveContinuingPeriodDays.description: The time (in days) that exclusive authority has been extended.

exclusivePeriodStartDate.description:
Start date of the exclusivity period.
The date is compliant with the ISO 8601 and is in the UTC format, e.g. 2009-06-15T13:45:30.0000000Z.

mapCertainty.description: Map certainty of the property location.

media.description: The media associated with the property provided by the advertiser

propertyId.description:
The identifier which uniquely identifies the property being advertised. 
This may be empty if the Address of property is poorly described

dateCreated.description:
The date/time the listing was created
The date is compliant with the ISO 8601 and is in the UTC format, e.g. 2009-06-15T13:45:30.0000000Z.

dateUpdated.description:
The date/time the listing was last updated
The date is compliant with the ISO 8601 and is in the UTC format, e.g. 2009-06-15T13:45:30.0000000Z.

firstName.description: First name of the agent contact.

lastName.description: Last name of the agent contact.

email.description: Agent contact email. Valid email address.

phone.description: Agent contact phone number. Valid phone number.

mobile.description: Agent contact mobile number. Valid mobile number.

domainAgencyId.description: The Domain agency ID. Must match an existing Domain agency ID.

listingProvider.description: A string identifying the source of the listing

providerAdId.description:
External Advertisement Id of up to 50 characters will be stored.
This value is correlated with actual Domain listing when it is created, and it should be unique for the listing provider. 
This value is case-insensitive (meaning AAAA will update aaaa).

carspaces.description: Number of car spaces divisible by 0.5.

summary.description: Headline of the advertisement. Any HTML will be stripped out.

description.description:
Description of the property. Allow up to 6000 characters in length. The following HTML elements are permitted: ```
,

,  ``` . HTML must be well-formed. Carriage Returns are interpreted as line breaks. Foreign characters must be HTML encoded, e.g., faade for faade

authorityExecutedDate.description:
The date on which the authority contract was executed.
The date must comply with the ISO 8601 and be in the UTC format, e.g. 2009-06-15T13:45:30.0000000Z.

propertyTypes.description: The property types (e.g. house, apartment/unit/flat, etc.).

exclusivePeriodDays.description: The time (in days) that the agent has exclusive authority to sell the property.

exclusiveContinuingPeriodDays.description: The time (in days) that exclusive authority has been extended.

exclusivePeriodStartDate.description:
Start date of the exclusivity period.
The date must comply with the ISO 8601 and be in the UTC format, e.g. 2009-06-15T13:45:30.0000000Z.

actionDate.description:
The date that this property was listed, sold or withdrawn. It is required if listing status is marked to be "sold, withdrawn, or listed".
The date must comply with the ISO 8601 and be in the UTC format, e.g. 2009-06-15T13:45:30.0000000Z. 
Only the date part will be saved, time part will be discarded.

PreMarket.v1.CreateOrUpdateListingRespon.description: Create or update pre-portal listing response.

yearRange.description: The range of year levels offered by the school.

icsea.description: The Index of Community Socio-Educational Advantage score for the school. This score is derived from a number of variables including parental school and non-school education and occupation, the schools geographical location and proportion of Indigenous students.

bottomSeaQuarter.description: The percentage of students positioned in the lowest socio-educational advantage quarter.

lowerMiddleSeaQuarter.description: The percentage of students positioned in the lower middle socio-educational advantage quarter.

upperMiddleSeaQuarter.description: The percentage of students positioned in the higher middle socio-educational advantage quarter.

topSeaQuarter.description: The percentage of students positioned in the highest socio-educational advantage quarter.

totalEnrolments.description: The total number of students, including both full-time and part-time students, who are enrolled at the school in the calendar year specified.

girlsEnrolments.description: The total number of female students, including both full-time and part-time students, who are enrolled at the school in the calendar year specified.

boysEnrolments.description: The total number of male students, including full-time and part-time students, who are enrolled at the school in the calendar year specified.
